      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. You won't find another one this clean! Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
