    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with a professional-grade ceramic coating and zero imperfections, chips, or swirls. Inside, the premium leather interior remains supple and fragrant, showing absolutely no signs of wear, creasing, or fading. Every electronic component, from the advanced infotainment system to the ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; a full, documented service history accompanies the car, with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time at a certified dealership. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory floor\u2014tight, responsive, and incredibly smooth. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48900.0,
